<h4><a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/418805565_260616">日本便利店开始测试 VR 控制机器人</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366357" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/6188283b-033b-49de-8a83-3b9cde62d808.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="2667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/6188283b-033b-49de-8a83-3b9cde62d808.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/6188283b-033b-49de-8a83-3b9cde62d808-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/6188283b-033b-49de-8a83-3b9cde62d808-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/6188283b-033b-49de-8a83-3b9cde62d808-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<p>澎湃新闻消息，日本科技公司 Telexistence 推出一款可通过 VR 控制的机器人 Model-T，现在已经在日本的罗森和全家便利店中测试使用，目前主要负责在便利店后方补货。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366358" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/robot-reponedor-controlado-forma-remota-persona-usando-realidad-virtual-2068905.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="807" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/robot-reponedor-controlado-forma-remota-persona-usando-realidad-virtual-2068905.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/robot-reponedor-controlado-forma-remota-persona-usando-realidad-virtual-2068905-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/robot-reponedor-controlado-forma-remota-persona-usando-realidad-virtual-2068905-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/robot-reponedor-controlado-forma-remota-persona-usando-realidad-virtual-2068905-1024x689.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>具体来说，Model-T 高约两米，机械臂有三根「手指」，能借此在货架上摆放饮料和罐头等产品，控制者可通过 VR 远程对其进行控制，适合这个需保持社交距离的时代。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1029747.htm">一加 7T「告白」亮相，全球仅此一台</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366359" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0bc17aaafaf2760.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="1097" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0bc17aaafaf2760.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0bc17aaafaf2760-360x658.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0bc17aaafaf2760-560x1024.jpg 560w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>快科技消息，为纪念一加 7T 谢幕，一加公布了一加 7T 新配色版本「告白」。一加 7T 告白全球只有一台，将通过特殊方式送出。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1029693.htm">富士发布 Instax Square SQ1，对自拍更友善</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366361" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/06z2YdiE08yP9W3f6z0U8Wc-1.1599856145.fit_scale.size_1028x578.jpg" alt="" width="1028" height="578" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/06z2YdiE08yP9W3f6z0U8Wc-1.1599856145.fit_scale.size_1028x578.jpg 1028w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/06z2YdiE08yP9W3f6z0U8Wc-1.1599856145.fit_scale.size_1028x578-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/06z2YdiE08yP9W3f6z0U8Wc-1.1599856145.fit_scale.size_1028x578-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/06z2YdiE08yP9W3f6z0U8Wc-1.1599856145.fit_scale.size_1028x578-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1028px) 100vw, 1028px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 消息，富士发布 Instax Square SQ1 即时照片相机，将平常 86×54 毫米大小的拍立得相纸尺寸换成 86×72 毫米，整体对自拍构图更友善。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366360" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ppgJKA5ys7Th4UY2yLCwLD-1200-80.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ppgJKA5ys7Th4UY2yLCwLD-1200-80.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ppgJKA5ys7Th4UY2yLCwLD-1200-80-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ppgJKA5ys7Th4UY2yLCwLD-1200-80-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ppgJKA5ys7Th4UY2yLCwLD-1200-80-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Instax Square SQ1 将根据环境光线条件自动调整快门速度和闪光输出。</p>
<p>此外，相机在镜头筒前还部配置了一面小镜子，作为取景参考。</p>
